body: Can we get rid of this?

replies.body: i vs'd him today, he was afk most of the game.

Defs a troll. If you look further he has good ARAM and custom game scores, no one would pay an elo-booster to play ARAM. 

His item builds are like too terrible for 20 minutes as well, you can get more than the starting items off just passive gold by 20 min.
Either a troll or elo boosted, I'd go for the latter.
